sequenceDiagram
    participant N as Navegador
    participant S as Servidor API
    N->>N: JSON.stringify({ title, completed })
    N->>S: POST /posts<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>Body: { title, completed }
    Note over N: fetch() retorna Promise pending
    S-->>N: 201 Created + JSON com id
    Note over N: Promise fulfilled<br/>resposta.ok = true
    N->>N: res.json() extrai o corpo
